
    A VILLAGER got the shock of his life last Saturday when he
awoke to sounds of someone breaking into his house – only to find it was two
elephants!According to Coconuts,
an unnamed 28-year-old living in Petani Village, northern Indonesia was fast
asleep when terrible sounds of the kitchen wall being smashed woke him.Panicking, he shouted to his neighbours for help. He
rushed into the kitchen, and there were two elephants eating his rice from where
